				<h1 id="headline" class="eza-title">
											
In Kentucky, a Democratic governor gains new fans: Republicans									</h1>
			</div>
		</div>

		
				<div class="row">
			<div class="editor-intro small-centered eza-body small-12 medium-11">
				<h2 class="title text-center">Why We Wrote This</h2>
				<div>
					
<p>As they confront a pandemic, governors are seeing their popularity soar. Kentucky’s Andy Beshear is winning plaudits for a calm, pragmatic approach that some see as a model for bridging the partisan divide.</p>				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
				<article id="story-content">
			
